OL,3,COne person dies in two-car crash
OL,5,FOne person has died following a two-
OL,6,Fvehicle crash in Omagh, Co Tyrone on
OL,7,FSunday.
OL,9,FDetective Inspector Dave Stewart, from
OL,10,Fthe Collision Investigation Unit,
OL,11,Fsaid: "Police received a report at
OL,12,Faround 9.10am of a collision involving
OL,13,Fa Volvo and a Mazda in the Clanabogan
OL,14,FRoad area.
OL,16,F"Officers, along with colleagues from
OL,17,Fthe Northern Ireland Ambulance Service
OL,18,Fand Northern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,19,FService attended. However, sadly, one
OL,20,Fperson was pronounced deceased at the
OL,21,Fscene."
OL,26,@sD@GOUxD@AOU}D@GO]
