OL,3,COne person dies in two-car crash
OL,5,FThe PSNI have said the Clanabogan
OL,6,FRoad, which was closed for a time, has
OL,7,Fsince reopened.
OL,9,FThe police have appealed for anyone
OL,10,Fwith information to come forward.
